  "commit_message": "Allow root params in App Shell (client)\n\nThe App Shell is the generic loading state for a route. It does not\ndepend on concrete param values, so it can be used for every navigation\nto a route before its params are known.\n\nWe've decided to special case root params: those that appear above the\ntopmost layout for a given route. These are typically used for params\nthat are low cardinality for a given session, such as the locale. So we\nallow them to appear in the generic part of the UI, even though t",
